    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK599">
<l>pariyatu kūrṅkōṭṭa tāyiṉum </l>
<l> yāṉai verūum pulitāk kuṟiṉ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Although the elephant has a large body, and a sharp tusk, yet it fears the attack of the tiger.</l>
